    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126200/extras/044f4194f00ceef499213c1db1307cf4.poster.avif?t=1771848535\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126200/extras/044f4194f00ceef499213c1db1307cf4.webm?t=1771848535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126200/extras/044f4194f00ceef499213c1db1307cf4.mp4?t=1771848535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Divine Wish</strong> 是一款具有独特贴纸系统的第一人称类Roguelike射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在激烈的战斗中生存下来，选择改变你能力和特性的贴纸，在动态的FPS Roguelike中与敌人的浪潮作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126200/extras/67007f74225999ee4b2a8cc46b4543b7.poster.avif?t=1771848535\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126200/extras/67007f74225999ee4b2a8cc46b4543b7.webm?t=1771848535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126200/extras/67007f74225999ee4b2a8cc46b4543b7.mp4?t=1771848535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FPS + Roguelike：爆炸性的组合</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Divine Wish</strong> 是一款高速的第一人称射击游戏，每次游戏都是独特的挑战。探索武器和神器的随机组合，适应新的威胁，在Boss战中证明你的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >速度、反应和准确性是你生存的关键技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有存档 - 每次死亡都会让你回到起点，但带来新的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于职业和随机神器系统，每次尝试都是独一无二的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>改变能力的贴纸</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Divine Wish</strong> 中没有传统的角色职业 - 你选择如何玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏开始前，你会获得一个贴纸，赋予你独特的效果并改变游戏玩法。但这并不简单 - 每个贴纸都会给你强大的加成和一个弱点，所以你必须明智地选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每第10波是一次史诗级的Boss战斗，将极限测试你的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的攻击和机制使你必须适应每一场战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难度的逐渐增加确保你不会轻松过关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有最优秀的玩家才能击败所有Boss并完成游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死亡只是开始</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就像任何Roguelike一样，每次游戏都是变强的机会。探索敌人，尝试贴纸，找到你完美的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Divine Wish</strong> 是Roguelike和FPS的爆炸性组合。准备好迎接挑战了吗？</p>",
